metadata.description: Blaize Holdings, Inc. provides artificial intelligence (AI)-enabled edge computing solutions. It offers AI edge computing products, including Blaize Pathfinder P1600 embedded system on modules, Blaize Xplorer X1600E EDSFF small form factor accelerators, Blaize Xplorer X600M M.2 small form factor accelerator platforms, Blaize Xplorer X1600P PCIe accelerators, Blaize Xplorer X1600P-Q PCIe accelerators, and Blaize Pathfinder 1600-DK embedded kits. The company also provides Blaize AI studio that delivers AI-driven application end-to-end data operations, development operations, and machine learning operation tools; and AI Studio marketplace, which allows users to browse and use AI/ML artifacts to run or share securely across their team and organization. It serves automotive, smart vision, and enterprise computing markets. The company was founded in 2010 and is headquartered in El Dorado Hills, California.
